method::gaussCurve
map the receiver onto a gauss function.

discussion::
Uses the formula:
code::
a * (exp(squared(this - b) / (-2.0 * squared(c)))) Default values: a = 1; b = 0; c = 1
::
Example code
code::
(0..1000).normalize(-10, 10).collect { |num| num.gaussCurve }.plot;
::


