method::lcurve
map the receiver onto an L-curve.

discussion::
Uses the formula
code::
a * (m * exp(x) * rTau + 1) / (n * exp(x) * rTau + 1)
::
This is used for smoothing values and limiting them to a range.
code::
(0..1000).normalize(-10, 10).collect { |num| num.lcurve }.plot;
::


